    <question>
        <prompt>How did the "convict lease system" affect Reconstruction?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Created a new form of forced labor targeting African Americans</option>
            <option letter="b">Reformed prison conditions</option>
            <option letter="c">Provided job training</option>
            <option letter="d">Reduced crime rates</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The convict lease system created a new form of forced labor by allowing businesses to lease prisoners, disproportionately targeting African Americans through selective law enforcement.</explanation>
